---
---

<section class="dayshift" aria-labelledby="dayshift-heading">
  <div class="dayshift-head" data-reveal>
    <h2 id="dayshift-heading">The difference shows up on your desk.</h2>
    <p>
      Not a new app to learn. The same work you do today, minus the parts a system now carries.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="dayshift-grid">
    <figure data-reveal>
      <img
        src="/images/desk-before.jpg"
        width="1536"
        height="1024"
        loading="lazy"
        alt="A desk buried in paper stacks, sticky notes, and unfinished admin"
      />
      <figcaption>Evenings spent retyping, chasing, and catching up.</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.12s">
      <img
        src="/images/desk-after.jpg"
        width="1536"
        height="1024"
        loading="lazy"
        alt="The same desk cleared, with one notebook and a coffee cup in morning light"
      />
      <figcaption>The same desk, once the admin runs itself.</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dayshift {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: calc(var(--section-pad-y) * 1.4) var(--section-pad-x);
  }

  .dayshift-head {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dayshift-head h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.6vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .dayshift-head p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--site-text-dim);
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .dayshift-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .dayshift-grid figure {
    margin: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--site-border);
  }

  .dayshift-grid img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .dayshift-grid figcaption {
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--site-text-dim);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--site-border);
    background: var(--site-surface-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .dayshift-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
